The eruption of the Hunga Tonga volcano disrupts flights to and from Tonga. (Radio New Zealand)Joaquin, expected to pick up forward speed when it turns north tomorrow, could hit the East Coast this weekend. While forecasts of the storm's trajectory are still uncertain, nearly every state from North Carolina to Connecticut is in the so-called "cone of uncertainty." North Carolina and New Jersey join Virginia in declaring states of emergency. (UPI), (Reuters)